| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-1177 — Recovery Inhibition (incransom)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: c5e1f8fd-2acc-5d9d-b6f2-17a5bdd64114"
